lead_paragraph: Coolness under pressure, a strong work ethic and never-say-die attitude makes Germany's Martin Kaymer one of the favorites for this month's British Open, according to Frenchman Thomas Levet.

headline.main: Kaymer's Composure a Major Trump Card, Says Levet
